{"tid":1215320,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(另謀出路）真心解決問題 - 警 方 倒 戈","createTime":"2019-06-13T06:46:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T07:39:21.000Z","uid":244636,"like":9,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b15e8496c06cc283248bd73f284a9939a791c810","tid":1215320,"uid":244636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">無左警察部隊 <br />\n政府無左枝矛同個盾 <br />\n逼佢地面對訴求</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要一少撮肯反思一下<br />\n只要一少撮肯放下屠刀 <br />\n其他警員就會慢慢覺醒</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好將修例問題轉移焦點去警民衝突</span><br />\n<br />\n要人轉軚 <br />\n首先 要表示理解、再作出可行建議<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOEk1Pj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOEk1Pj.png&h=34b3182e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J0DOuk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J0DOuk.png&h=1dc22bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZcnOrf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZcnOrf1.png&h=7e57b707&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUeQEA2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUeQEA2.png&h=07ece2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 佢地累了<br />\n 2. 林鄭唔抵得幫 <br />\n3. 佢地應該選擇暈 跟住sick leave<br />\n 4.唔好再施以過份、不合理暴力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔想再見到暴力行為<br />\n唔想再見到警民對立<br />\n唔想再見到社會分裂</span><br />\n<br />\n長遠啲睇 警方倒戈 等政府知道 警察唔係盲撐<br />\n水能載舟 亦能覆舟<br />\n長遠啲睇 承認612過分武力 幫下尋日被拘捕既人士 可能會判無罪<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">可能會有負皮 但我覺得僵局對我地不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"731a5d7a7c8021f12fbd3bca2d332c3b842303d4","tid":1215320,"uid":34698,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦<br />\n成班都係狗黎"},{"pid":"48e76e9cc0328661085295850327dfaed2d6144a","tid":1